description._content: Description: View of Korno (3,000 feet above sea level) showing mixed Aleppo Pine and Cypress Forest on the northern side of the mountain, elevation ranging from 2,400 to 3,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: Forest near Yomaristra Pass with limestone cliffs and Chamberlayne's partially finished road in the foreground, Elevation about 2,600 feet, Lapithos Forest. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
